title: Tim.Wintons.The.Turning.2013.x264.mp4
description:
Tim.Wintons.The.Turning.2013.x264.mp4:

1) The.Turning.2013.PDTV.x264-W4F

  The Turning was heavily cut down and rearranged for broadcast
on ABC1, debuting on February 23, 2014. Running for 
approximately 90 minutes (as opposed to the 180-minute 
theatrical cut), only eight of the original 17 stories were included:
 "Reunion", "Aquifer", "On Her Knees", "The Turning", "Long, 
Clear View", "Commission", "Cockleshell", and "Sand".  

2) The.Turning.2013.Missing.Chapters

The remaining nine stories "Abbreviation", "Big World", 
"Boner McPharlin's Moll", "Damaged Goods", "Defender",
 "Family", "Fog", "Immunity" and "Small Mercies".
